      "releaseNotes": "Meta AI has a new look and new capabilities\n• Faster, more accurate responses\n• Up-to-date answers grounded in what’s trending across your favorite apps \n• Find, compare, and shop products\n• Advanced reasoning mode for complex questions\n• Add photos, docs, and spreadsheets for richer, more relevant answers",
